MidCon Corp, a unit of OccidentalPetroleum Corp, said that effective May 1,Dan Grubb will be the unit's president and chief operatingofficer, taking over the title of president from O.C. Davis,who will remain chairman and chief executive officer.    MidCon said Robert Hodge, Midcon senior vice president forplanning and administration, will take over for Grubb aspresident of Midcon Services when he assumes his new duties.    Also, Midcon said that Philip Gasparac, Midcon senior vicepresident and chief financial officer, will take on theadditional responsibilities of planning, rates and jointventures. Reuter&#3;